#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
Remove selected function records from `.gcno` coverage notes files.

The tool walks `.gcno` files under the current directory, parses the note
records, and drops any function record whose name appears in one of the input
config files. When a function is removed, the following records that belong to
that function are also skipped so gcov/gcovr no longer report coverage for
code that the linker discarded.
"""
